title: Beware of Security Alert-Themed Malicious Emails that Steal Your Email Logins

content.raw: A sophisticated phishing campaign is currently targeting email users with deceptive security alert notifications that appear to originate from their own organization’s domain. The phishing emails are crafted to resemble legitimate security notifications from email delivery systems.
